Feature: OIDC login (PKCE) happy path
  As a user of {{project_name}}
  I want to authenticate via the configured OIDC provider
  So that I can access protected screens of the app

  Scenario: User signs in successfully
    Given the user is on the login screen
    When the user taps "Sign in"
    And the user authenticates against the OIDC provider in the external browser
    Then the app receives an access token
    And the access token is persisted in secure storage
    And the user is redirected to the home screen

  Scenario: Authentication fails (network error)
    Given the user is on the login screen
    And the device is offline
    When the user taps "Sign in"
    Then the app shows an error message
    And the auth_bloc emits AuthError
    And no token is persisted
